text: Nurdavletovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Zirgansky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 102 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Meleuz, 9 km from Zirgan. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Nurdavletovo
